prompts.frontCover: A vibrant comic book cover illustration for a greeting card. Lao Lao and Jordan from the photo are rendered as dynamic comic book heroes. Lao Lao, in her blue sweatshirt and black pants, is depicted as a superhero named "Super Lao Lao," striking a powerful, confident pose with one hand on her hip and the other pointing forward with a joyful, heroic smile. Jordan, in his tan hoodie and dark pants, is her loyal sidekick, comically struggling to hold an impossibly large, teetering stack of birthday presents all wrapped in colorful, patterned paper. He has a funny, exasperated expression as he tries to balance the gifts. The background is a stylized, explosive burst of bright yellow and orange, with classic comic book action lines radiating outwards. Bold, thick black outlines define the characters and elements, with halftone dot patterns used for shading. In the center of the card, within a white, jagged-edged speech bubble, the text "Happy Birthday to my Favorite Superhero!" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is energetic, humorous, and full of action. Flat 2D artwork.
